nodes.text: The year 36,019 before the Battle of Yavin, also known as the year 434 after the Tho Yor Arrival, was a period of time in the pre-Republic era. By that year, the Je'daii Order on the planet Tython had established Padawan Kesh, one of their Je'daii Temples, and Nordia Gral was serving as Padawan Kesh's first Temple Master.
